name: Deep Cosmic Mining DAO
description:
Bitcoin mining in affordable moon-rock-sized chunks. Don't want to commit 10s of thousands of dollars to ASIC mining, but still want to be part of a Bitcoin mining community? Deep Cosmic Mining is for you!

We run the best bitcoin mining hardware, and a smart reinvestment strategy means every ETH today will ensure hashrate for the community long into the future!
